{"tid":110798,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"橋本環奈「想追自己的夢」所屬團體Rev宣布3月解散","createTime":"2017-02-07T03:17:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-07T16:30:15.000Z","uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"15211142d36bdc4990e08d3d123e85ce4d741771","tid":110798,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T03:17:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2317/d2317125.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2317%2Fd2317125.jpg&h=75272bdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Rev. from DVL是以福岡為主要活動地的地方女團。<br />\n<br />\n日本女偶像團體Rev. from DVL在2011年成立，2013年時因為成員橋本環奈的一張「奇蹟美照」打開知名度，成為日本國內的人氣地方女團。怎料，經紀公司6日突然宣布團體將在3月31日解散，成員們也一一透過社群網站證實消息，讓許多粉絲驚慌失措。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img-s-msn-com.akamaized.net/tenant/amp/entityid/AAmG78n.img?h=64&amp;w=80&amp;m=6&amp;q=60&amp;u=t&amp;o=t&amp;l=f&amp;f=jpg&amp;x=581&amp;y=232\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-s-msn-com.akamaized.net%2Ftenant%2Famp%2Fentityid%2FAAmG78n.img%3Fh%3D64%26w%3D80%26m%3D6%26q%3D60%26u%3Dt%26o%3Dt%26l%3Df%26f%3Djpg%26x%3D581%26y%3D232&h=7cc78872&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nRev. from DVL官方網站6日發表公告，表示團體將在3月31日正式解散，其中原因包括大埔承峰1,522呎享清靜泳池園景有成員想轉換跑道、有人想要繼續念書，大家各自擁有不同的夢想，決定要在這個階段去實現，最後的公演將會分別於29日、31日舉行；粉絲這也才發現，原來5日成員上傳的手勾手團結照別有含意，像是在傳遞道別訊息。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2317/d2317135.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2317%2Fd2317135.jpg&h=625c3f9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲成員昨日不約而同都發了勾手的照片。（圖／翻攝自秋山美穗、橋本環奈、今井瞳、古澤早希）<br />\n<br />\n人氣王奧運站維港灣5座高層C室橋本環奈稍早也在部落格證實消息，她表示自己今年3月就要從高中畢業了，再加上從去年開始個人活動相當多，很難調配時間，「我也有了想要追尋自己夢想的想法，而打從心底支持我的成員們，我真的很愛她們，讓我的心更加堅強。」橋本透露成員們雖然一邊要忙課業、一邊要忙工作，但都很盡心想做好最後的演出，希望粉絲能夠到場支持。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2317/d2317126.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2317%2Fd2317126.jpg&h=fba82c3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲橋本環奈在部落格寫下對於解散的心情。<br />\n<br />\n消息曝光後，有許多粉絲直呼「太突然」、「覺得很寂寞」、「希望大家都能幸福」；不過也有網友表示早就料到團體撐不久：「畢竟是靠橋本環奈在撐。」砲轟公司從不用心經營團體活動。事實上，橋本環奈爆紅之後，引起過不少風波，像是傳出成員眼紅她的人氣鬧不合、粉絲抗議公司太偏心等，甚至有人不知道橋本有隸屬的團體、戲稱Rev.為「橋本環奈與她的小夥伴們」。"},{"pid":"310b755454ebf408cc43e733893ff29ac00e5400","tid":110798,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T08:39:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6a3b5a92c7fb0598a6147db64aafe1896a93daa","tid":110798,"uid":27578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T08:41:54.000Z","msg":"解散之後可以下海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d09e1b6676338d48fffcdde2c6b91f194316a2c","tid":110798,"uid":11880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T08:47:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>解散之後可以下海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n梁烈唯你都岩睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c27286e1cba312861e8a03359b16c194850d5be","tid":110798,"uid":34470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T08:47:53.000Z","msg":"其中原因包括大埔承峰1,522呎享清靜泳池園景有成員想轉換跑道"},{"pid":"0ef74482d5ee50c6136c82c0cbf04eecee5d52c8","tid":110798,"uid":70538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T08:48:48.000Z","msg":"人氣王奧運站維港灣5座高層C室橋本環奈?"},{"pid":"1cdc7e57c5a30c32604f9eae65933101c63b5d57","tid":110798,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T10:53:31.000Z","msg":"橋本環奈與她的小夥伴們<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d61a506360157028869b90406cdef4f7b172efb","tid":110798,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T16:30:15.000Z","msg":"其他人無人識 好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}